cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about image classification using attention mechanisms and global context. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other possible sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
